\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2837121 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 Reserved, was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2043071 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 No, she was frustrated, you know, with so many children. You
 couldn't talk to my mother, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2837121 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 You mean she had so much to think about to worry her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2043071 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 
Yes, yes, and she couldn't be - you know, she seemed to be always ... no, one could never talk to her. I can remember my mother ... only wishing she would, and
 I can remember praying - this is the truth - if God would make me ill so my mother would talk to me and kiss me and have a little affection because she had ... You know, when I look back upon it she had so much to do and so little that you can understand
 
her. Because you know what children are, they do things that they shouldn't do, tear your clothes and do things, you know, that you shouldn't do and with doing all that and washing and ironing and ... I mean, you can't look back on your childhood and thin
k
 it was happy because it wasn't. Because my mother had lines across the kitchen and the washing was all .... I can never remember the kitchen ever being free of washing. I mean, my father would have to come home and have his meal and sit there and there w
as all wet washing hanging on the lines, and then the next day or so after that it was mangled, and then there was always the airing. We had no garden to dry it out.
