No, I don't think they ... We did have - what did they call it, now? some lesson which was to do ... which they don't have now ... Physiology, they used to have that, about all the bones and all the rest of it, which they don't ha
ve at school now. I can remember that when I was quite little and I've never forgotten it. I can remember the vertebrae, the back bone and your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949612\charrsid2325820 f}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 ibula and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949612\charrsid2325820 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 ibia, and all those things, learnt all those at ... I forget what lesson, not Optic lesson ...
