\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949612\charrsid2325820 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 es. Three pound a week, and then I had to pay the rent and everything out of that. Mm.
