ll the - the council house, which - for twelve years we lived there. Or eleven or twelve years. Mm. Yes, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2837121 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7866333\charrsid2325820 So you want to live in the house with his mother?
